  <data name="HowHeading" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>How it works?</value>
  </data>
  <data name="HowSub" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Three steps separate you from finding the perfect offer. No more manually browsing dozens of sites.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Step1Title" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Choose a category and enter a phrase</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Step1Body" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Looking for a car, apartment or specific product? Choose a category, type what you're looking for and set filters.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Step2Title" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Set an alert once</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Step2Body" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Define your criteria as an alert. The system will automatically monitor dozens of portals without your involvement.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Step3Title" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Receive notifications</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Step3Body" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>When a new listing matching your alert appears, you instantly get a notification in the app. Be first.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="FeaturesHeading" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>What does Wyszukiwacz offer?</value>
  </data>
  <data name="FeaturesSub" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>All the tools for effective listing search in one place.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Feature1Title" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Parallel search</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Feature1Body" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>One query searches all supported portals simultaneously. No need to visit each site separately.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Feature2Title" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Alerts and notifications</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Feature2Body" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Set an alert for any phrase and category. When a new matching listing appears, you instantly see it in the notifications section.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Feature3Title" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Lightning-fast results</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Feature3Body" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Results from multiple portals are collected in real time and presented in a clear, unified view.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Feature4Title" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Clear offer view</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Feature4Body" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Compare offers from different portals side by side – price, location, date added – in one consistent interface.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Feature5Title" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Filters and categories</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Feature5Body" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Cars, apartments, shopping – each category has dedicated filters tailored to the specifics of that market.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Feature6Title" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Secure account</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Feature6Body" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Your data and alert settings are securely stored on the server and accessible after logging in from any device.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="CategoriesHeading" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Listing categories</value>
  </data>
  <data name="CategoriesSub" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Four main markets covered by Wyszukiwacz – each with its own set of portals and filters.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="CatCarsTitle" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Used cars</value>
  </data>
  <data name="CatCarsPortals" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>6 automotive portals</value>
  </data>
  <data name="CatCarsBody" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Search for used and new cars on the biggest Polish automotive portals simultaneously. Compare prices and filters in one place.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="CatFlatsTitle" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Apartments and houses</value>
  </data>
  <data name="CatFlatsPortals" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Largest real estate portals</value>
  </data>
  <data name="CatFlatsBody" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Browse apartments, houses and plots for sale or rent. Filter by city, price and area – results from Otodom and other portals.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="CatShoppingTitle" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Online shopping</value>
  </data>
  <data name="CatShoppingPortals" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Products and price monitoring</value>
  </data>
  <data name="CatShoppingBody" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Search for products on Amazon and other shopping platforms. Track prices and get an alert when a product gets cheaper or a new offer appears.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="CatWorkTitle" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Job offers</value>
  </data>
  <data name="CatWorkPortals" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>5 job portals</value>
  </data>
  <data name="CatWorkBody" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Search for jobs on Pracuj.pl, JustJoin.IT, NoFluffJobs and more. Filter by position, location, seniority and contract type – results from multiple portals at once.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="FaqHeading" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Frequently asked questions</value>
  </data>
  <data name="FaqSub" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Everything you need to know before your first login.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Faq1Q" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>How does Wyszukiwacz work?</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Faq1A" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Wyszukiwacz automatically searches dozens of Polish listing portals simultaneously. You enter a phrase, choose a category and filters – and we collect results from OLX, Otomoto, Otodom, Amazon and many others. Instead of visiting each portal separately, you see all results in one place.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Faq2Q" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Which listing portals are supported?</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Faq2A" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>We support the largest Polish listing portals: cars – Otomoto, OLX, Gratka, Sprzedajemy, AutoScout24, Autocentrum; real estate – Otodom and OLX; shopping – Amazon. The portal list is regularly expanded.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Faq3Q" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>How do I set an alert for new listings?</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Faq3A" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>After logging in, go to the Notifications section in the sidebar. Enter the phrase you are looking for, choose a category and portal. From that moment the system automatically monitors portals and notifies you when a new matching listing appears.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Faq4Q" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Is Wyszukiwacz free?</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Faq4A" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Yes, registration and use of Wyszukiwacz is completely free. You can search listings on all supported portals and set an unlimited number of alerts at no cost.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Faq5Q" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Can I search Otomoto and OLX at the same time?</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Faq5A" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Yes – that's the main advantage of Wyszukiwacz. One query in the Cars category searches Otomoto, OLX, Gratka and other automotive portals in parallel, showing results in one unified view.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Faq6Q" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>How quickly will I get a notification about a new listing?</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Faq6A" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Notifications are generated as soon as the system detects a new listing matching your alert. This lets you react as one of the first interested parties – which is crucial especially in popular categories such as apartments or cars.</value>
  </data>
